abstract: |
  This research is an examination of MTCars dataset using R programming. The research performs relationships between MPG and different factors. The data was gotten from Motor Trend US magazine from 1974. Information incorporates fuel utilization and 10 parts of car configuration plan and execution for 32 vehicles and data plot with 32 discernments on 11 factors.
